('61017','21297','5','Unique opportunity! 9-hole golf course with hotel and 3 detached villas'),
('61018','21298','5','This 4 star golf hotel with 22 suites and double bedrooms, was constructed out of a historic building dating back to the 17th century and is set on a flat plot of 180 hectare, situated in the heart of the island. The beautiful property in manor house style boasts a gourmet restaurant, a garden restaurant, outdoor pool, a tennis court, a heliport and a well-kept private 9-hole golf course with bunker, chipping and putting green and driving range.\r\nFurthermore, you can produce your own wine, there are Cabernet, Merlot, Syrah, Riesling  and Callet grapes on the organically farmed vineyards which belong to the property.\r\nA spacious wellness area with sauna, fitness room and massage rooms invites your guests to relax and find some recreation.\r\nIncluded in the price are 3 newly built detached villas, each of them set on a plot of 18,000 m² with private pool and own vineyard.\r\nIf you would like to have more information about the property, please send us an email with your postal address and a landline number and we will contact you directly.'),
